        Copy this code and do
        
            import hanging_threads
        
        If a thread is at the same place for SECONDS_FROZEN then the stacktrace is printed.
        
        This script prints
        
        --------------------    Thread 6628     --------------------
          File "hanging_threads.py", line 70, in <module>
                time.sleep(3) # TEST
        --------------------    Thread 6628     --------------------
          File "hanging_threads.py", line 70, in <module>
                time.sleep(3) # TEST
        
        
